metadata.name: #1 The Forbidden Big Apple
metadata.description:
"The Path Less Traveled" is a curation of 25 moments taken during the life of Elliott Chau, each with a unique story that paints the narrative of his journey as a photographer. This is his invitation for you to join along.

To read the full story behind "The Forbidden Big Apple" visit www.thepathlesstraveled.io.
